text-align: justify;\">Havuz arayüzüne ait yukarıdaki tanımlamada dikkatimizi <span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&lt;T </span><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(127,0,85); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">extends</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"> Yedeklenebilir&gt; </span>tip parametresi çekmektedir. Böylece Havuz arayüzünü sadece Yedeklenebilir arayüzüne erişmiş yapılar için genelleştirmiş / sınırlandırmış (bounding) olduk. </p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">NesneHavuzu Sınıfı </span></b></p><p><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(127,0,85); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">public</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(127,0,85); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">class</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"> <span style=\"background: silver 0% 50%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\">NesneHavuzu</span>&lt;T </span><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(127,0,85); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">extends</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"> Yedeklenebilir&gt; </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">      </span><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(127,0,85); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">implements</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\"> Havuz&lt;T&gt; {</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">      </span><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(127,0,85); font-family: &qu